Subsonics					TYPE:General					PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Bardic Music																																												PRESKILL:1,TYPE.Perform=10																								DESC:Your music can affect even those who do not consciously hear it.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.112	BENEFIT:You can produce music or poetics so subtly that opponents do not notice it, yet your allies still gain all the usual benefits from your bardic music. Similarly, you can affect opponents within range with your music, but unless they can see you performing or have some other means of discovering it, they cannot determine the source of the effect.
Tactile Trapsmith				TYPE:General																																																																																					DESC:You can rely on your rapid reflexes and nimble fingers instead of your intellect when searching a room or when disabling a trap.																																										BONUS:SKILL|Search,Disable Device|DEX-INT																																																																																																																																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.112	BENEFIT:You add your Dexterity bonus (rather than your Intelligence bonus) on all Search and Disable Device checks.
